HEADWORD: Japanned
<hw>Ja*panned"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Treated, or coated,
with varnish in the Japanese manner.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Japanned leather</b></col>,<cd>leather treated with
